A retro 1960s space race propaganda poster style illustration showing a determined red panda astronaut in a vintage spacesuit floating through a cosmic void filled with geometric patterns of dots and dashes resembling morse code or binary. The panda clutches a large mechanical keyboard against its chest like precious cargo. Saturn and distant nebulae glow in warm oranges and teals behind. The composition uses bold, flat color blocks with halftone textures and dramatic diagonal rays emanating from the astronaut, evoking Soviet-era space posters but with a playful, absurdist twist. No text or letters anywhere in the image.
